The Katsura River in Arashiyama. Clouds don&apos;t usually light up like this in the evening, so it was a special treat after a day of overcast weather. Mt. Arashi &lt;em&gt;(Arashiyama)&lt;/em&gt; and the Togetsu Bridge are on the right side of this picture, a 24-shot HDR panorama.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;
  嵐山の桂川です。普段、夕方に雲がこんな風に光ることはないので、曇り空の一日の後の特別な楽しみでした。この写真の右側が嵐山と渡月橋です。この写真は24枚撮りのHDRパノラマである。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Panoramas" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">The Katsura River in Arashiyama. Clouds don&apos;t usually light up like this in the evening, so it was a special treat after a day of overcast weather. Mt. Arashi (Arashiyama) and the Togetsu Bridge are on the right side of this picture, a 24-shot HDR panorama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08242-HDR-Pano-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2205_A7R08242-HDR-Pano-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kawai Kanjiro‘s House・河井寬次郎記念館</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220515/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kawai Kanjiro‘s House・河井寬次郎記念館" /><published>2022-05-15T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2022-05-15T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kanjiro</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220515/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
